Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=10}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.48,0:00:02.27,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.11,0:00:06.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That leg is all beat up.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I know, but what else am I\nsupposed to do? It's all I've got.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.66,0:00:15.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Better bring my crutch, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.33,0:00:19.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But I told you I'd be your leg for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I never asked for that in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's got you all pouty?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.47,0:00:33.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But seeing you rely on that old beat-up thing\nso much does make me a little jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.89,0:00:34.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.81,0:00:41.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Losing out to that glorified peg leg\nbesmirches my good name as a robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.56,0:00:45.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have to prove that these high\hspecs\nof mine aren't just for show!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.94,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}, I—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, no thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't you dare get any funny ideas, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.04,0:00:59.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You coming, or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are we...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,School's gonna start without you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.46,0:01:05.42,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're coming, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wait for me! I have to be your leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're gonna want one of these.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gotta take notes in class.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.69,0:02:50.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Thank you! Now I can start keeping logs!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Logs?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.03,0:02:58.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nonko told me to do it so I can have a record\nof what happened on any given day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{*}Sounds low-tech.{*She told a robot that?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't you just store\nthat information in your memory?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.62,0:03:07.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But apparently this would help me develop\nmore human-like memory storage faculties.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.17,0:03:14.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Maybe having you lose your memories was\nan intentional effort to make you seem more human.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.30,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're so smart, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Clearly, my memory loss is proof\hpositive\nof my astronomically high—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's not go that far.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,"Going to school with Natsuki{**-san}."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.35,0:03:33.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No peeking! That's a violation\nof the Robot Autonomous Privacy Act!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Welp.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,We just have to cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.95,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,With my incredible long jump skills,\na gap like this isn't even a—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yeah, not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If we swim, we'll get our clothes wet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Not what I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.21,0:03:52.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Kids get in and out every day, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's gotta be some easier way to—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.84,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Wh-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere, hitman!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.35,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We know all about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,You're an evil hired gun\nfrom the mainland, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.94,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,We've heard the stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.94,0:04:13.11,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,You have a rifle hidden in your crutch,\nand you're not afraid to use it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.53,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Oh. That's the game we're playing, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If you wanna take on Natsuki{**-san},\nyou'll have to get through me first!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.74,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Back off, pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.74,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Pipsqueak?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You heard her, pipsqueak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.08,0:04:26.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not you too, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.58,0:04:30.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got very important\nbusiness at your school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.83,0:04:34.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If you don't want to eat lead from my machine crutch,\nyou'd best get outta my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,R-Ririka, what do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,T-Tactical retreat! Run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.39,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,After 'em, Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.39,0:04:42.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Mwahaha! You'll never take us alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.50,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Weren't {\i1}we{\i0} supposed to be the bad guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We have to follow them!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.88,0:05:19.51,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,With my flawless long\hjump technique,\na gap like this is—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.51,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.64,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Ririka, look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.44,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Aah, I forgot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This floor's totally empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.37,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So that's where they were.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.96,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All right, boys and girls! Time for class!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Minamo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.51,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Take your seats, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.51,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Minamo{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.51,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,We've got trouble! The hitman's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Run for your life!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.01,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.10,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.02,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Isn't he the hitman? And—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,The pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm no pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.86,0:06:23.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's got a name, and it's\nBootleg Humanoid McToaster the Third.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You mean Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You really came!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna stick around\nafter class starts, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where's the teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.20,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.37,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,You're real clueless, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.25,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Minamo{**-chan}'s our teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,She teaches us language arts,\nmath, science, social studies, everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.13,0:06:40.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.22,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All our teachers already evacuated to the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,'Cause, you know,\nthere's barely any students left...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.14,0:06:55.69,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,My dad wants me to shut everything down\nand do the paperwork to transfer to the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I mean, you can hardly call\nthis place a functioning school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.36,0:07:04.49,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,We don't even have electricity,\nso we can only have class when it's light out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.49,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I know these kids deserve better, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'll be fine either way,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but you should at least {take up a collection just to -p}send them to\nthe\hmainland so they can get a decent education.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They have aid programs for disaster victims, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.88,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Shut up, dude. Don't act like\nyou understand a single thing about us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.72,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What would you even know?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.93,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You're just some fancy-pants elite\nwho abandoned us to go to the Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I didn't abandon anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.22,0:07:33.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I studied hard and enrolled in the Academy\nso I could make a difference.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.14,0:07:33.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.56,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Then get started on that already.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.27,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Ever since you came back,\nyou've just been moping around on your boat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.19,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,At least we're making an honest effort here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.11,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.15,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sound just like the mainlanders.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.28,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You talk a big game about making a difference,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.28,0:07:50.83,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,but all you do is sit on your ass\nwhile the rest of us suffer.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.75,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Atri! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Bye! See you all tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.93,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Looks like you've made some new friends, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.93,0:08:14.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes. School is much more fun than I was expecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.64,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.27,0:08:21.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I had this feeling that school was a very sad place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just silly. Right, Natsu{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sorry. I should've just stayed home.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,No, you didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.66,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ryuu{**-chan} knows that, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.79,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,He's just had some bad experiences\non the mainland, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He has?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.04,0:08:45.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Those kids lost their parents,\nso he tried bringing them over to the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.97,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But, you know, folks over there\nare also struggling to get by,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.97,0:08:52.93,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,so the kids ended up getting ostracized at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san} looks sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Cheer him up when you get home, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.23,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.07,0:09:07.86,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You know, Natsu{**-kun},
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.78,0:09:13.03,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'd really appreciate it if you came back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not like there's anything for you to teach me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.21,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's plenty for you to teach us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd Atri go?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She said she was going on ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You gave her your permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, guess I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She wanted to prepare a nice surprise for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A nice surprise?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It's okay! You don't have to panic!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.86,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sure she just wants to make\na nice dinner for you and—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.03,0:09:52.86,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,H-Huh? I can't see...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.67,0:10:14.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I, uh, thought it might cheer you up\nif I made you a tasty dinner...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,How does cooking lead to a mess like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,W-Well, as I've said before,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.39,0:10:24.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,in a way, making human-like mistakes\nis actually proof of my stupendously high specs!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's not even {\i1}humanly{\i0} possible\nto screw up this badly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.73,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Maybe some part of her is malfunctioning?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Could be. And I don't have any way\nto repair her, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better chuck her back into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wanna explain how you caused\nthis catastrophe, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,U-Uh, that's easy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You see, the truth is...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.46,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.46,0:10:50.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm a top-secret lethal autonomous robot\ndeveloped by a foreign government.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.01,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I infiltrated this country\nto take it down from within...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But the war came to an end\nbefore I could carry out my mission.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I lost not only my homeland,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,but my very reason for existence.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.36,0:11:17.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There I found myself, a poor,\nlonely killing machine with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But in my moment of greatest despair,\nNonko found me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.16,0:11:29.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,She took me in, gave me a name,\nand a new purpose.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And that was...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Doing housework...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.17,0:11:38.51,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But as a specialized combat unit,\ncontrolling my strength is—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.18,0:11:39.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Humanoids can lie, can they?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.93,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes! But of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec, baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.69,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All of that was a lie?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.40,0:11:56.07,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't you think this violates\nthe Humanoid Anti-Abuse Act?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She'll survive. She doesn't even need food, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.57,0:12:02.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If you ask me, a robot lying to\nits master is a {\i1}much{\i0} bigger problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Objection, Your Honor!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,One, I am a robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Two, I am hopeless at housework.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,From these two indisputable facts,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,simple deductive reasoning\nleads to the eminently logical conclusion
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,that I am almost certainly a deadly—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then hit me with your best shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A war machine like you's\ngotta at least have some missiles, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Y-You asked for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Rocket pun—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.98,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'd better not.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.98,0:12:36.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I must obey the Three Laws of Robotics,\nand I can hardly guarantee your survival.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You live to see another day, Natsuki{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why is running your mouth\nthe one thing you're good at?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Because my speech apparatus is super high—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You know, Atri{**-chan},\nI think you've really cheered Natsu{**-kun} up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.46,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Here, come eat with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.55,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I think this egg came out nicely!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't waste our food!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Très bien!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,See you two tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.94,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Please pack extra eggs for lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What makes you think you're getting any?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'll graciously taste test your food\nand deliver my discerning verdict.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,A feat only made possible\nby my downright preposterous specs!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.78,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd better update my logs...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.54,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.75,0:13:29.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.04,0:13:37.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I think I left my logbook at school!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't this wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.55,0:13:50.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. Logs are of vital importance!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'd think you wouldn't forget it, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It sure is dark...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nighttime generally is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,D-Did you see that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Natsuki{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That was totally weird, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We don't have electricity on this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.96,0:14:17.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Aw, are you a widdle scaredy-cat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Poor baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.92,0:14:23.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's all right. When we get back you can cuddle\nwith me again as much as you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're just too precious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.01,0:14:34.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wait! Violence isn't the answer, Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,The floor's flooded with seawater.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It was totally dry earlier, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,High tide...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Of course. {\i1}That's{\i0} why there wasn't\nanything on the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I-I knew I saw something earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Switching to high-sensitivity mode!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It looks like a person! Atri, away!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey! Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So, what about the light?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There was nobody there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You said you saw a person.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What if it was a... ghooost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,They might've gone upstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Didn't know you can access the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Looks like nobody's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Maybe it really was a ghooost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're a robot. Stick to the scientific.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's them! My eyes never lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.05,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Huh? The hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.10,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hey, it {\i1}is{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ririka!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.65,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.90,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I live here, stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh? You live {\i1}here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.24,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Not just me, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.37,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Ryuu{**-chan} and Tooru, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.70,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,All our houses sunk into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.33,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Aw, couldn't the wind have held out a little longer?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.84,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I was almost done reading this, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,An electricity textbook...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.26,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I've got nothing better to do at night,\nso I bring this up from the library.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.35,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Thought there might be a way\nto bring electricity back to the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.02,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.36,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What're you doing here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.61,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Here. 'S not much,\nbut I brought a few snacks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.36,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.53,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Any batteries?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.78,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Sorry. Looked all over, but I couldn't find any.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.12,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.16,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.29,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Listen, don't strain yourself\ntryna read that. It's bad for your eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.92,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Get some sleep soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.17,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.67,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,This is life for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.22,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Those of us who have nothing,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.47,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,we get chased off the mainland\nbefore we can accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.97,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,But start off in a better position,\nand apparently you get whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.60,0:17:21.27,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We want to study so we can change something,\nbut we don't even get to do that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Guess it's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}! Where were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, when you're done writing that,\ncan you help me spin the turbine outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Sure, but why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I have an idea I wanna test.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Should I keep going?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah! Gimme more juice!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're a combat robot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.39,0:18:46.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ngh... this is borderline robot cruelty!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Looks like efficiency really does\nsuffer on such a small scale.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.86,0:18:54.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But a bigger turbine would come\nwith its own problems...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}, can I stop yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuki{*}ii{*-saaan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}, you dirty boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}? Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Get ready soon, or we're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Have you been working all night long?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,At the Academy, we called it Tuesday.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm bringing something\nfor show-and-tell today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Mind carrying it for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.67,0:19:56.13,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All right, class, I've invited a special guest\hlecturer\ntoday for a super special lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,A guest lecturer?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.26,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Let's give him a warm welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.48,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Oh. The hitman.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Keep your disappointment to yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I've got feelings too, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.48,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.86,0:20:17.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Some stuff I scrounged up around town last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.53,0:20:22.41,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A lightbulb, a motor, a pinwheel, and a dry cell.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Aw, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.79,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,That ain't gonna last long without wind, genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's why it gets thrown out with the trash,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,even on this island,\nwhere we need everything we can get.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But with a little ingenuity, even junk like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.85,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,It's so bright!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.81,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah, so long as the wind holds up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But what if we could store\nthe electricity we're generating?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.66,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,No way! You can store wind energy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Takes some extra effort, but yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.33,0:21:07.00,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You want a medal or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.50,0:21:12.92,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,There's only so much electricity\na tiny little pinwheel like that can make.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.50,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Stop getting their hopes up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're not wrong. But what if it wasn't so tiny?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.43,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What? You think you're gonna\nbe able to build us a giant turbine?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.35,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Like hell that's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is it really out of the question?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Besides, wind isn't the only way\nto generate electricity.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.60,0:21:34.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's thermal power, water power, nuclear power,\ngeothermal power, and not to mention...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.15,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,You can make electricity with the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.70,0:21:46.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Lucky for us, this school is sitting right in it,\nand the second floor gets flooded at high tide.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.54,0:21:48.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We can take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.21,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.29,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Get real, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.04,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What about materials, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.04,0:21:56.67,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Everything halfway useful\non this island is already—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.09,0:21:57.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.05,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.76,0:22:05.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{=11}There's a whole treasure trove of goodies\nout there ripe for the taking!

